都有新游戏更新。就像给孩子放空大脑一样。能让他们保持活力和娱乐。我觉得我们绝对值回票价了"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "cid": "7580098817593803534", "createTime": 1764879312, "createTimeISO": "2025-12-04T20:15:12.000Z", "text": "I bought it for Christmas for my kids, I’ve got 4 between the ages of 4-11. I’ve seen good reviews and I’ve played the demo in stores. Idc about the subscription. Almost all gaming system have them.", "diggCount": 1, "likedByAuthor": true, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 1, "uid": "7472560827511620654", "uniqueId": "rachelstewart9316", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p19-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast8-avt-0068-tx2/a73453b3b6fe6c411ad1d204551d08f1~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=4af1bab4&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=m3XE0N6CVVUGjaD2vK7w2Vuw77o%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast5", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "我圣诞节给孩子买的，有 4 个，年龄在 4-11 之间。我看了评价，也在店里试玩了演示。我不在乎订阅费。几乎所有游戏机都有。"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "cid": "7588001526238495501", "createTime": 1766719308, "createTimeISO": "2025-12-26T03:21:48.000Z", "text": "I did for same ages. Its cool just need to get the subscription now to have full access but well see how that goes after a year use and if we will re subscribe to it but it was a great hit", "diggCount": 3, "likedByAuthor": false, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 0, "uid": "6607107926246162437", "uniqueId": "berthaayala11", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast5-avt-0068-tx/734998221850201297