.tiktokcdn.com/img/user-avatar-musically/a7bf0acad5ac2dc4bcccee018a47fcd7~120x256.image", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "孩子们还在玩，我拥有它。这都两年了。"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "cid": "7578373514358604558", "createTime": 1764477609, "createTimeISO": "2025-11-30T04:40:09.000Z", "text": "No skipping", "diggCount": 0, "likedByAuthor": false, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 0, "uid": "6807617521790551045", "uniqueId": "toniduggar", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast5-avt-0068-tx/959200c62f947b4eca3a5414f848ad22~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=edd86014&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=vLknNUePG8sN9cAkp%2B4H8gXMEos%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast5", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "不能跳过"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "cid": "7578151211845845815", "createTime": 1764425847, "createTimeISO": "2025-11-29T14:17:27.000Z", "text": "my grand kids are 12...7 ...and 3.. and they love it..fun for adults also just bought before Thanksgiving and they play it constantly", "diggCount": 0, "likedByAuthor": false, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 0, "uid": "6992394154190685190", "uniqueId": "leeleesuncatcher", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-maliva-avt-0068/a6ee9a6e8b8c61172bec746feea14b9c~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=a2f14cdd&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=KMHvmKRVaQvrHMSTFGeiq3weNlU%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast5", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "我的孙子们12、7和3岁，他们很喜欢它…大人也觉得好玩，感恩节前刚买的，他们一直在玩。"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "cid": "7587574743545840415", "createTime": 1766619937, "createTimeISO": "2025-12-24T23:45:37.000Z", "text": "💔💔💔", "diggCount": 0, "likedByAuthor": false, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 0, "uid": "7393068243587449899", "uniqueId": "t4c0m3x1c4n", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast8-avt-0068-tx2/ee15ca4c93481e582a1f94437a9e8c0f~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=93f15733&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=a1bEd%2BlHBsqjjjU4%2BDdgCbs2AgA%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast5", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "💔💔💔"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "cid": "7585386425072993054", "createTime": 1766110442, "createTimeISO": "2025-12-19T02:14:02.000Z", "text": "Not a mom but my cousins got it not worth it to be paying about 100 a year after tax to play all the games instead of 4 with msot of them being glorified carnival or arcade games like whack a mole stuff like that better off getting a switch and mario party for the same experience", "diggCount": 1, "likedByAuthor": false, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 0, "uid": "7543502651028947981", "uniqueId": "ry4n.s0", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast8-avt-0068-tx2/1ec47f87722ec1f9fe2e953856d4ac49~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=f0ba9757&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=qFmoYshAXopBieGeS5%2FVF%2Bh7DuI%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast5", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "不是当妈的，但我的表亲们买了，不值。为了玩游戏要交 100 左右一年（含税），而只能玩 4 个游戏，其中大部分还是些打地鼠之类的嘉年华或街机游戏。还不如花差不多的钱买个 Switch 和马里奥派对来玩。"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "cid": "7578504568058364727", "createTime": 1764508143, "createTimeISO": "2025-11-30T13:09:03.000Z", "text": "I have the same question.. I have a 3 and 5 year old… do we just wait or do we get it?", "diggCount": 0, "likedByAuthor": false, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 1, "uid": "6813445021783147526", "uniqueId": "dkcardillo", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast5-avt-0068-tx/debde142ce9c34f52d8d1b5d94feeada~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=59cccac2&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=%2FBqWGUhSKHU2XdB5fwXFF3%2F0sus%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast5", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "我有同样的问题… 我有 3 岁和 5 岁的孩子… 是等一下还是现在就买？"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "cid": "7576886636663915294", "createTime": 1764131412, "createTimeISO": "2025-11-26T04:30:12.000Z", "text": "I just bought it two days ago and have it to my kids early 😆 it is absolutely as good as it looks. I have 3-10 year olds and they all love it.", "diggCount": 1, "likedByAuthor": true, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 1, "uid": "7406927625707488298", "uniqueId": "amanda.anderson24", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast8-avt-0068-tx2/9ca5367d82ee7ec1664bd81ead59c405~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=21ed0903&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=YL0DaPOseARslFv9pmaZheUUsb8%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast5", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "我两天前刚买了给我孩子当提前的礼物😆，效果跟看起来一样好。我孩子3到10岁，都特别喜欢。"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "cid": "7576640917050852127", "createTime": 1764074223, "createTimeISO": "2025-11-25T12:37:03.000Z", "text": "Yes. I did it for Bday in October. He's 8. The play pass is worth it too!", "diggCount": 2, "likedByAuthor": true, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 1, "uid": "7240652628831863854", "uniqueId": "ash_lynn51", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast5-avt-0068-tx/5d0192fac6e8fb94cc946c1cce47c80f~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=86940c00&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=x9rm730PpmZmZNafuNeMBjdZNLY%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast5", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "是的。我在10月为他8岁生日买的。那个通行证也很值！"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@all_mels/video/7576334352582331662", "cid": "7576426931513541407", "createTime": 1764024383, "createTimeISO": "2025-11-24T22:46:23.000Z", "text": "I have 5 year old twins and a 2 year old and I did. Fingers crossed", "diggCount": 2, "likedByAuthor": true, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 1, "uid": "6790889832652882946", "uniqueId": "makingbabyschuler", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-maliva-avt-0068/4cac